162
00:13:34,209 --> 00:13:35,239
Jus sayurmu.

163
00:13:38,310 --> 00:13:41,020
Keluarlah dan minum, Yeong Woong.

164
00:13:42,650 --> 00:13:44,050
Astaga.

165
00:13:44,989 --> 00:13:47,690
Aku menyanjungnya agar dia tidak minder di depan para gadis,

166
00:13:47,690 --> 00:13:50,020
